1
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:09,039
Die, all of you!

2
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,840
Is this the immortal?

3
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,050
Lei Long.

4
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,000
Between heaven and earth,

5
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:49,400
everything is intertwined with cause and effect.

6
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,200
You are drowned in past grudges,

7
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:54,370
blinded by the evil desires in your heart,

8
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,000
and acting recklessly on this land.

9
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,640
But do you know that

10
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,600
the karma you created

11
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,880
is not borne by you alone?

12
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,810
Those who care about you

13
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:09,020
are also silently suffering from this pain.

14
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:13,770
Those who care about me?

15
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,800
I, Lei Long,

16
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,640
in this world,

17
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:22,320
have long been a loner.

18
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:26,120
Where are those who care about me?

19
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,240
Your brother

20
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,900
has not yet reincarnated.

21
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,160
My brother?

22
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,440
Where is he?

23
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,040
Do you still remember

24
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,340
in the past,

25
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,240
when you were a shaman,

26
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,960
the mountain god you devoutly worshipped?

27
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,560
You should have fulfilled your duty as a priest,

28
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,890
using your body as a pact

29
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:46,460
to connect the realms and reach the gods,

30
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,770
protecting the peace of this land.

31
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,400
But you were bewitched by your inner demons

32
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,280
and slaughtered every living soul in the village.

33
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,880
Because of this grave mistake,

34
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:58,680
the mountain god was implicated

35
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:00,940
and stripped of his divine title.

36
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,610
For a hundred miles around,

37
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,680
there is no longer any divine protection.

38
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,440
Drought demons are wreaking havoc,

39
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,840
and floods are frequent.

40
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,440
People are displaced,

41
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,280
and the land is filled with grief and suffering.

42
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,080
Your brother,

43
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,660
to atone for your monstrous sins,

44
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,370
abandoned the path of reincarnation,

45
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,839
and with a wisp of a remnant soul,

46
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,640
incarnated as a mountain slave.

47
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,840
Enduring the punishment of lightning strikes

48
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,600
and the suffering of wind erosion,

49
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:28,200
he took upon himself all the illnesses and disasters

50
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,460
of millions of people.

51
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,920
Holding the rain-praying umbrella you left behind,

52
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:35,180
he guards the mountaintop day and night,

53
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,659
just to help you atone.

54
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,490
In his heart,

55
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,220
his brother...

56
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,280
He is not the

57
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:45,300
heinous monster people speak of.

58
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:46,720
He is still

59
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,400
the hero who keeps the region safe

60
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:50,080
by fighting for justice.

61
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:54,370
He continues the ending you left unfinished.

62
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:56,220
And what about you?

63
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,340
What are you doing?

64
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:03,880
Immortal,

65
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,840
please don't let my poor brother

66
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:10,240
suffer this ordeal anymore.

67
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,640
I'll take the blame for what I've done.

68
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,240
Let me take

69
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:16,080
full responsibility for this matter.

70
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,160
Everyone

71
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:19,440
has their own destiny.

72
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,480
His suffering for you

73
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,660
is his destined tribulation.

74
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:24,860
Saving him,

75
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,050
delivering him,

76
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,770
is saving yourself,

77
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,860
delivering yourself.

78
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,360
If you sincerely follow the right path,

79
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,159
are you not also delivering him?

80
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,640
What you should do

81
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,480
is entirely up to you.

82
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,159
Brother.

83
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,200
Brother,

84
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,040
I...

85
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:02,800
It's fine.

86
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:03,650
Brother,

87
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,320
there is so much suffering in the world.

88
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,180
Over the years,

89
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,560
I've seen too much

90
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,730
for far too long.

91
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,160
But the karma of all this suffering...

92
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,490
It will never change because of you and me.

93
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,640
Come with me.

94
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,160
Let's finish

95
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,250
what we started.

96
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,020
We will do it

97
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:22,240
together.

98
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:42,840
Immortal.

99
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,040
I am one of the Four Demons of Tumen,

100
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,440
Tu Luohua.

101
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,850
I have been looking for you.

102
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,440
You must...

103
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,760
You must be careful.

104
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,520
I have my own destiny.

105
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,360
Go.

106
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,560
Four Demons of Tumen.

107
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,440
Thank you, Master.

108
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,500
Thank you, Master.

109
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:46,160
Thank you, Immortal. Thank you, Immortal. Thank you, Immortal.

110
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,440
The Immortal has appeared.

111
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,480
Thank you, Immortal.

112
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,610
I am not an immortal.

113
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,260
Don't thank me.

114
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,440
If you want to thank someone,

115
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:56,640
thank Feilu.

116
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,040
Why?

117
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:02,440
Now,

118
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:05,440
although the demons have been eliminated,

119
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,360
but in the future,

120
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,960
we do not know what risks there will be.

121
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:08,920
You should still

122
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,170
make yourselves stronger.

123
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,880
Thank you, Immortal.

124
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:15,560
Tonight,

125
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,820
I will stay here for the night.

126
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:20,490
I'll hit the road early tomorrow morning.

127
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,560
Sneaking around.

128
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:38,400
Come in.

129
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:44,880
What is it?

130
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:45,640
Master,

131
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:47,160
where are you going?

132
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,160
To sell medicine.

133
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,040
Where to?

134
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,740
None of your business.

135
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:51,500
Master,

136
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,810
why don't you

137
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:53,880
take me with you?

138
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,010
I want to join you

139
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,770
to uphold justice everywhere.

140
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:57,800
I told you,

141
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,570
I'm just a medicine seller.

142
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,100
Then I'll sell medicine with you.

143
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,600
I can be your servant.

144
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:04,560
Washing clothes, cooking,

145
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,800
I'm good at everything.

146
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:06,200
No.

147
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,280
Master.

148
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,480
I'm going to rest.

149
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:14,880
Kid,

150
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,060
close the door.

151
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,080
Immortal,

152
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,600
you saved us.

153
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:43,140
We can never repay you.

154
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,440
We gathered some dry rations overnight.

155
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,440
If you don't mind,

156
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,840
please accept them.

157
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,970
Please accept them.

158
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,480
Our meeting

159
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,020
is merely fate.

160
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,210
Since it is fate,

161
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,690
there's no need to be so polite.

162
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,880
You already have it hard enough.

163
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,040
Keep these things

164
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:00,970
for yourselves.

165
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:03,800
Immortal,

166
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,250
please accept this.

167
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,740
For such a great favor,

168
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:07,960
if we don't thank you,

169
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,280
we won't have peace of mind.

170
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:11,880
Please accept it.

171
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,400
Please accept it.

172
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:14,000
Immortal,

173
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,160
please accept it.

174
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,760
Please accept it, Immortal.

175
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,480
Just consider it as buying my goods.

176
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,620
Distribute these peace amulets.

177
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,660
They will keep you safe and sound.

178
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:43,040
Thank you, immortal.

179
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,640
Thank you, immortal.

180
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,480
Thank you, immortal.

181
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:49,920
Thank you, immortal. Thank you, immortal.

182
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,120
Thank you, immortal.

183
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:51,880
Thank you.

184
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,720
Ping Jieqiang, Hai Hui.

185
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:24,920
Ping Jieqiang.
